	<h3>Council Programs 2022 - 2023</h3>


	<p>
		<u><span style="font-size:18">SHINING ARMOR & SILVER KNIGHT AWARDS</span></u><br>

		Worthy District Deputies, Grand Knights and Council Program Chairmen Recognize deserving and outstanding members of your council by awarding
		them the Shining Armor Award and Silver Knight Award.  Visit our State Website to learn more about this programs and print nomination forms.
	</p>

	<p><span style="font-size:18">1. <u>SHINING ARMOR AWARD PROGRAM:</span></u></p>
	<p>This is a Supreme Council Award. Program is open to all new members:  Requirements:  Within the year, the new member must: </p>
	<ol type="a">
		<li>Worked on 3 Council Service Programs</li>
		<li>Attended at least 3 Council Business meetings</li>
		<li>Received his 2nd & 3rd  Degrees</li>
		<li>Meet with Council Insurance Representative</li>
		<li>Recruited one new member</li>
	</ol>
	<p>Upon completion of the requirement, the new member must submit his competed form to the Grand Knight for approval.</p>


	<p><span style="font-size:18">2. <u>SILVER KNIGHT AWARD PROGRAM: </span></u></p>
	<p>This Program is open to all 2nd and 3rd Degree members:  Requirements:  Within the year, the member must. </p>
	<ol type="a">
		<li>Attended at least 3 Business meetings</li>
		<li>3rd Degree member in good standing (FS attest).</li>
		<li>Insurance member (FS attest) or date meeting with Field Agent</li>
		<li>Participate in 3 Programs with the Council;</li>
		<li>Recruit at least 2 new members.</li>
	</ol>
	<p>Upon completion of the requirements, the member must submit his completed form to the Financial Secretary  and Grand Knight for approval.</p>

	<p><u>Award Submission</u>: The Grand Knight will then submit the form to:</p>

